# â­ **5. Important MongoDB Methods**

### âœ” Show Databases

```js
show dbs
```

### âœ” Use Database

```js
use bookstoredb
```

### âœ” Create Collection

```js
db.createCollection("books")
```

### âœ” Insert One

```js
db.books.insertOne({
  title: "A Tale of Two Cities",
  author: "Charles Dickens"
})
```

### âœ” Insert Many

```js
db.books.insertMany([
  { ... },
  { ... },
  ...
])
```

---

# â­ **6. Querying Documents**

### âœ” find() â€“ returns multiple documents

```js
db.books.find()
```

### âœ” findOne() â€“ returns one document

```js
db.books.findOne({ title: "Harry Potter" })
```

---

# â­ **7. WHERE clause equivalent in MongoDB**

### âœ” Equals

```js
db.collection.find({ key: value })
```

### âœ” Less than

```js
db.collection.find({ age: { $lt: 25 } })
```

### âœ” Greater than or equals

```js
db.collection.find({ marks: { $gte: 80 } })
```

### âœ” AND

```js
db.collection.find({
  $and: [
    { age: { $lt: 25 } },
    { marks: { $gte: 80 } }
  ]
})
```

### âœ” OR

```js
db.collection.find({
  $or: [
    { age: { $lt: 25 } },
    { marks: { $gte: 80 } }
  ]
})
```

---

# â­ **8. Updating Documents**

### âœ” updateOne()

```js
db.books.updateOne(
  { title: "Harry Potter" },
  { $set: { author: "J.K. Rowling" } }
)
```

### âœ” updateMany()

```js
db.books.updateMany(
  { genre: "fantasy" },
  { $set: { rating: 5 } }
)
```

---

# â­ **9. Deleting Documents**

### âœ” deleteOne()

```js
db.books.deleteOne({ title: "The Alchemist" })
```

### âœ” deleteMany()

```js
db.books.deleteMany({ genre: "drama" })
```

---

# â­ **10. Dropping Collection & Database**

### âœ” Drop collection

```js
db.books.drop()
```

### âœ” Drop database

```js
db.dropDatabase()
```

---

# â­ **11. Advanced: Count, Sort, Limit, Skip**

### âœ” Count

```js
db.books.countDocuments()
```

### âœ” Sort

```js
db.books.find().sort({ year: -1 })
```

### âœ” Limit

```js
db.books.find().limit(5)
```

### âœ” Skip

```js
db.books.find().skip(3)
```

---

# â­ **12. Aggregation Pipeline (Very Important!)**

### âœ” Average

```js
db.books.aggregate([
  { $group: { _id: null, avgYear: { $avg: "$publication_year" } } }
])
```

### âœ” Group by genre

```js
db.books.aggregate([
  { $group: { _id: "$genre", count: { $sum: 1 } } }
])
```

### âœ” Group + Sort

```js
db.books.aggregate([
  { $group: { _id: "$genre", count: { $sum: 1 } } },
  { $sort: { count: -1 } }
])
```

---

# â­ **13. Projection (Select only required fields)**

### âœ” Include selected fields

```js
db.books.find({}, { title: 1, author: 1, _id: 0 })
```

### âœ” Exclude fields

```js
db.books.find({}, { ISBN: 0 })
```

---

# â­ **14. Text Search (Requires index)**

### âœ” Create text index

```js
db.books.createIndex({ title: "text", author: "text" })
```

### âœ” Search

```js
db.books.find({ $text: { $search: "road" } })
```

---

# â­ **15. Regex Search**

### Find titles starting with â€œTheâ€

```js
db.books.find({ title: { $regex: "^The", $options: "i" } })
```

